{"tid":1685284,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前線同和理非嘅手足，我比你地一個不可能嘅任務","createTime":"2019-10-31T12:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T12:43:26.000Z","uid":321228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c7ccda608d4d1f96f5cfaaa7b2fe48b37d9c38b","tid":1685284,"uid":321228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:37:36.000Z","msg":"如果前線手足有機會同班狗狗埋身肉搏果陣，試下除佢地面罩。如果成功左，佢個狗樣就會比全世界睇到，到時就會比人起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信班狗被除面罩果下點都會縮一縮，咁樣可以幫其他手足爭取時間，好過淨係攞遮打狗又唔痛又冇用。<br />\n<br />\n當然和理非都可以咁做，睇邊隻唔順眼就除邊隻，但前題一定要人影住，方便起底。<br />\n<br />\n反正除面罩又唔犯罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最多咪坐幾個鐘就放人。<br />\n<br />\n最好嘅情況就係捉漏單狗同得幾隻狗，全部人包圍佢地，唔好打佢地，淨係除面罩，打佢地幾日就好番，但比人起底就唔同講法。<br />\n<br />\n呢個做法夠和理非啦，冇人反對掛。既然肉體上做唔到傷害，咁就要從內心入手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2028b62c12e1e6543a9ba042cd24e84c04db71","tid":1685284,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:38:20.000Z","msg":"（公投）11.2好似有活動撞左時間<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1685128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1685128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n入嚟討論下幫手投票順便推post上熱門比多啲人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117edd26ea668345508a445b0281aab7876a05f6","tid":1685284,"uid":181527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:40:50.000Z","msg":"即刻告你襲警"},{"pid":"6e78b5b61dc2c23abf934c0defe3a2e10a31b303","tid":1685284,"uid":321228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:41:17.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e09e91facc82e89ac43041d5b88266f6a8f7af","tid":1685284,"uid":321228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"117edd26ea668345508a445b0281aab7876a05f6","tid":1685284,"uid":181527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:40:50.000Z","msg":"即刻告你襲警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:43:26.000Z","msg":"最多有衝突果陣先除囉，情況混亂冇人知邊個做嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}